description: Getting ready to make your life just a little sweeter! We are a mobile pastry shop bringing the sweets to you.Pin-up Pastries is all about fun, and the most delicious pastries you'll ever pop in your mouth! We specialize in Cake Pops, Macaroons, Cupcakes and the famous Whoopie Pie, the cupcake that sold it's soul to the devil!We can create our "sinfully sweet" treats in a variety of flavors, colors and designs. Have an idea? Let us know and we will do our best to make it a reality. We can put together something special for any occasion.And because we are mobile, we come to you. Don't let us being in Tucson stop you from enjoying our scrumptious desserts...we will deliver to Phoenix and surrounding areas for a small fee.
name: Pin-Up Pastries
